articles.author: Arjun Kharpal
articles.title: Tesla expects to raise Model 3 prices in Europe after higher EU tariffs on China EVs - CNBC
articles.description: Tesla said it may have to increase the price of the Model 3 sold in the EU after the bloc said it could impose higher tariffs on electric cars imported from China.
articles.content: Tesla on Thursday said it will likely increase the Europe prices of its Model 3 vehicle from July 1 after the European Union said it could impose provisional higher tariffs on electric cars imported … [+1434 chars]
